These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: indian, mexican
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, disco
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, surfing
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the mexican is in an even position##4
3. the fan of disco is the indian##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Nationality      | indian  | mexican   |
| Music-Genre   | disco     | folk   |
| Sport         | surfing | cycling |
| Transport     | jet-ski | taxi    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, cabbage
The people have 2 different hobbies: gardening, chess
2 different pets are kept: dog, rat
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, mechanic
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is the mechanic##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | avocado     | cabbage |
| Hobby   | chess | gardening  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| Job     | bartender   | mechanic    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, australian
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur
2 different pets are kept: frog, lizard
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, rose
1. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the dutch is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Nationality    | australian     | dutch |
| Job         | entrepreneur | accountant    |
| Pet         | frog         | lizard        |
| Flower   | sunflower         | rose    |

